<https://w3id.org/codefeedback-kg/id/busqueda_binaria> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "def binaria(xs, x):\n    lo, hi = 0, len(xs) - 1\n    while lo <= hi:\n        m = (lo + hi) // 2\n        if xs[m] == x: return m\n        if xs[m] < x: lo = m + 1\n        else: hi = m - 1\n    return -1" .
